item.title: Char API (Stream)
item.description: We offer a free API to allow people to add there own Chat commands to a stream to pull info. NB; !Commands are suggestions / what (Mach) Uses, It doesn’t really matter how it gets fired, aslong as the right thing gets sent to the API This is NOT a chatbot, this is the baseline for a command that can be run from a chatbot… !rp The Default repose is the help text
